ss smaller than the background rate level. We demonstrate for\nthe first time how detailed multi-instrument studies of solar flares can be\nperformed with STIX.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jan 2022 15:24:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
